        AI engines extract product data from structured markup, listing content, and data feeds — then synthesise that data into
        shopping answers. <strong class="text-white">AI optimization for product listings</strong> is the discipline of ensuring your
        product data is structured, complete, and written in a way that AI systems can accurately extract, represent, and
